&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Help global companies embrace the latest private cloud infrastructure, Linux and cloud native operations, and open source applications. Our team applies expert insights to real-world customer problems, enabling the enterprise adoption of Linux Ubuntu, OpenStack, Kubernetes and a wide range of associated technology.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
