&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 300;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 300;&quot;&gt;Bachelor’s or equivalent in Computer Science, STEM, or a similar degree&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
